{"tid":2340380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港（25/12）增57宗確診，25宗源頭不明","createTime":"2020-12-25T11:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T13:49:01.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30854492dc3b7d8136a7c642992fd617e126d4bd","tid":2340380,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417910&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=154aae27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417910&h=8c827dea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417910</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港新增57宗新冠病毒確診個案，25宗屬源頭不明。<br />\n<br />\n仁濟醫院郭玉章夫人護理安老院一名院友確診，患者周一曾經外出覆診，平日會到護老院四樓跟其他院友進食；當局會將四樓院友及數名工作人員送往檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘花園大廈玉蓮臺再多一個單位有人確診，連同早前的個案，大廈四個單位有人確診，累積八人染疫，當局對大廈居民發出強制檢測公告。<br />\n<br />\n一名在伊利沙伯醫院、有長期病患的95歲男病人今日確診，同日病逝；本港累計死亡人數增至136人。<br />\n<br />\n另外有約五十宗初步陽性個案，包括聯合醫院一名外科病房的護士，她鄰居早前確診，醫院四名職員被列為密切接觸者。"},{"pid":"2cd49483b1655020eef47f6e53d61b7b6e2a596d","tid":2340380,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"></span>"},{"pid":"94e63c8b05f706ae0a8d1a9a9406bb9e2d044c48","tid":2340380,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"冇事了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5882899619aacd00feba5d847b48993602d15c55","tid":2340380,"uid":81757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"冇事了 +111111"},{"pid":"76133c26a16867e96294ad716c81b67c7a2dc97e","tid":2340380,"uid":198539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"開番gym未呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"cce968c2e4e47730f6dba8c3b7